==0.6.0==
''More flexibility''

This version will have a [[en/Archive/Manual/New Bridges|Full flexible track/road layout under bridges]], [[en/Manual/Drive-through Road Stops]], [[en/Archive/Manual/NewGRF Houses]], [[en/Archive/Community/Custom Bridgeheads]], [[en/New Economy and Balancing|New Economy and Balancing]], Newcargos, Newindustries, more NewGRF support and lots of more nice features, also maybe PlayStation Portable port comes in this release.

''(More information: [[en/Archive/Lists/Roadmap 0.6]])''

==0.7.0==
''The first stand-alone version''

Maybe in a few years we'll have released the first stand-alone OpenTTD version. This means that we'll have put our own, completely new graphics, sound and music in the package.

